# Tailwind and tokens

- Define colors, fonts, and spacing for the visual identity in [`src/styles/main.css`](src/styles/main.css) via `@theme` and/or CSS variables; in markup prefer Tailwind classes referencing those tokens (`bg-apz-*`, `text-apz-*`, etc.).
- Avoid inline `style=""` except on **Canvas** and necessary dynamic values.
- Classes added from JavaScript must be **literals recognizable by the scanner** or defined in CSS (e.g. `.apz-scrub-span-2`) so they are not purged at build time.
